Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拿可…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一起喝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}夹缝的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔过下这种生活也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计你在想着 真是没有紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就放松一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不这样 这个国家也是全年战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家尽是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论重复几次都不知吸取教训
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是愚蠢又悲哀的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔 加上暴动 东部也真是够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是东部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北边和西边也尽是暴动与国境战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也和南边的阿耶鲁戈 西边的古雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在国境线附近一直有小冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方也是有大国德拉古马存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是尸体堆起的山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时不会颠覆国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危险的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是现在的大总统布拉德雷上任以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才如此倾向于军事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 真受欢迎 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人跳很无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会跳舞这门艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去和那边的孩子们一起跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个孩子开始考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体链成这种东西时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就这么大年纪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为父亲 说他几句也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使教训他几句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要赎罪的现实也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪就是罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有期望这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 他是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是脚 手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是心脏 全给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我唯一的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将克塞鲁克塞斯一夜之间毁灭的天上之石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有这个的话 说不定就能取回阿尔的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生 上面命令你研究的东西到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能追求那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是恶魔的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会看到地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可追求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会怨恨你的 马可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石的材料是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是脆弱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏惧黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样一时忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是非常弱小的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 作为我们珍贵的资源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们起到关键的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能找到真实中的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是为了链成贤者之石的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我看看你的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为假肢捡了条命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱刀连钢铁都能贯穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很丢脸 但是我们的确输了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会说其实是三人兄弟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 快点杀掉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这种身体也算人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果承认你们不是人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等于承认了我的弟弟不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的弟弟是人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不想杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 我们兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从懂事开始就偷盗 破坏 杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到变成这个样子还能被当人看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是给你留个回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令我们守护这里的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险 真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 48号 说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你这个呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们差点就把重要的人柱杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人柱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人的师傅或许能成为人柱的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你是人柱候补
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这里死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想让我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奥尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊修瓦尔我们干的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是哪里的哪个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干这种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你们干的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个国家和所有国民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造巨大的链成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了制造贤者之石 有错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实已经知道了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没对任何人说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有什么改变吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复相同错误的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 每次都只会逃避的无力模样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 贤者之石是核
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧 人工制造的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正全员都要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为去冥界的礼物给你们看个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肚子里养着怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把周围的东西全吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做出这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你有最强的盾一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有最强的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说军队里有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是指军队本身很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造人造人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类没有最强的矛 也没有最强的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且容易被小事缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得无法重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的人类能对人造人做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样也不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是你们的模样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那种伤势 为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把皮肤烧掉堵上伤口了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两三次差点晕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管来几次你都赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 让你把秘密说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲上脑门的血稍微流掉了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子冷静多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想抵抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃这一拳乖乖地睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:16:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体 确实有许多不便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不便不等于不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有理由让你觉得我可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哥哥用链金术延续的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果否定现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等于否定哥哥 否定链金术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信链金术的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可恶 止不住血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能为您效劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰芳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被踩在脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会无数次地面对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是挣扎而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不试试看怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起知道却不行动的家伙要好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使爱德和阿尔 还有大家都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要那么拚命吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使为了人类行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他们不还是会自己死去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是白忙一场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就抱着最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻逃到别的地方去才是上策吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良心的责备吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的感伤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使再怎么为他们着想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 谁都不会接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 你自己的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类只是普通的资源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管也会自己繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有你行动的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这么做了 又会有什么改变？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个现实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依旧弱小的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确实很弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能为变强而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使对你来说是徒劳的几步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那每一步确实积累起了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的人保护更下层的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是弱小的人也能做到那一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我 兰芳更有觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让谁死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把真理那混蛋踢飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从那里把你的身体夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 一定能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挣扎着活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类才能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 你的心还在动摇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在利塞布尔一同度过的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对眼前的巨大力量感到恐惧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼 你可以离开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.53,0:24:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失去了信奉的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就倒下吧 弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.51,0:24:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是决战的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力战斗吧 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.21,0:24:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第28话 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我由于不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:48.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:52.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:02.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:06.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:12.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:23.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:27.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:32.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:36.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:41.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:48.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:52.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:56.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:01.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:38.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:45.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:48.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:51.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:56.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:01.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:06.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:11.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:17.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:22.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:28.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:33.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:39.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:44.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:49.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:52.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:56.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福

